    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """Advancements in the fields of genetics and genomics have provided profound insights into both the structural and functional dimensions of plant genomes. These revelations not only deepen our understanding but have also equipped us with novel tools and methodologies, facilitating more efficient and cost-effective research strategies in crop plant studies. To fully harness the potential of these innovations, there?s an imperative to converge diverse disciplines like structural genomics, transcriptomics, proteomics, metabolomics, plant physiology, and plant breeding. A plant breeder?s paramount objective is to analyze the genetic composition of individual plants, selecting those genotypes that exhibit the most promising traits within breeding populations. Early selection yields better genetic enhancement. The traditional marker-assisted breeding approach has now evolved into genomic assisted breeding, largely attributed to the plummeting costs of individual genotyping.
This course delves into Genomic Selection (GS) or Genomic Prediction (GP), a cutting-edge breeding methodology leveraging genome-wide molecular markers to predict breeding values for complex quantitative traits.
Our goal for this course is to furnish participants with a foundational understanding of the quantitative and statistical aspects essential for routine GS application. Emphasizing hands-on learning, this course will revolve around practical plant breeding exercises using the R platform.

Upon completing this course, participants can expect the following learning outcomes:
Gain a foundational grasp of plant breeding and quantitative genetics in the context of enhancing crops.
Acquire the essential knowledge to construct Genomic Selection/Genomic Prediction mod- els from the ground up.
Implement supervised machine learning techniques within plant breeding initiatives."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/j.isidro%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/j.isidro%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Mejora Asistida por Genómica"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/CE02> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE02" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Utilizar sistemas operativos, programas y herramientas de uso común en biología computacional, así como, manejar plataformas de cómputo de altas prestaciones, lenguajes de programación y análisis bioinformáticos/ Utilizing operative systems, software and tools commonly used in computational biology, and working with high throughput platforms, programing languages and bioinformatics tools."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/CE03> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE03" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Analizar e interpretar bioinformáticamente los datos que se derivan de las tecnologías ómicas, y proponer soluciones bioinformáticas en relación a dichos datos/ Analyzing and interpreting bioinformatically data derived from ?omics technologies, and proposing bioinformatics solutions according to such data."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/CE05> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE05" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Utilizar herramientas de biología computacional para el análisis genómico, incluida la genómica comparativa y biología evolutiva/ Using computational biology tools for genomics analyses, including comparative genomics and evolutionary biology."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/CE10> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE10" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Conocimiento de las técnicas de representación del conocimiento reutilizables y modelos de razonamiento en entornos centralizados y distribuidos a utilizar en la resolución de problemas que impliquen conducta inteligente/ Knowing reusable techniques for knowledge representation and reasoning models in centralized and distributed environments, and when to used them for problem solving."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/CG02> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG02" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Familiarizarse con el trabajo y los métodos de la Biología Computacional en condiciones reales, adquiriendo la capacidad de diseñar aplicaciones/experimentos de forma independiente y describir, cuantificar, analizar y evaluar críticamente los resultados obtenidos/ Becoming familiar with the work and methods in Computational Biology in real situations, acquiring the capacity of design applications/experiments in an independent manner and critically describe, quantify, analyze and evaluate the obtained results."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/CG03> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG03" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sepan aplicar los conocimientos adquiridos y su capacidad de resolución de problemas en entornos nuevos o poco conocidos dentro de contextos más amplios (o multidisciplinares) relacionados con el area de la Biología Computacional/ Provide students with the ability to apply the acquired knowledge to solve problems in new environments within ample or multidisciplinary contexts in the field of Computational Biology."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/CT03> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT03" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Tener compromiso bioético y profesional y respeto por la sostenibilidad ambiental/ To have bioethics and professional awareness for environmental sustainability."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/RA13> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA13" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Conocer los últimos desarrollos, técnicas y herramientas en bioinformática y biología computacional aplicada a los programas de mejora genético"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/RA14> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA14" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Conocimientos para aplicar las nuevas tecnologías genómicas a proyectos reales de mejora genética de cultivos"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000026/2025-26/RA15> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA15" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Conocimiento de las herramientas genómicas para caracterización de bancos de recursos genéticos y su utilización en programas de mejora."@es .

